front.title: Victory-Class Star Destroyer
front.gametext: May add 4 pilots, 6 passengers, 1 vehicle and 3 TIEs. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Adds 1 to your total power in battles at related planet sites.
front.lore: Commissioned by the Old Republic at end of the Clone Wars, Rendili StarDrive's Victory-class starship is atmosphere-capable but has a low sublight speed.

combo: Victory-Class Star Destroyer + Imperial Helmsman Draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.
